2004
01:17:40,319 --> 01:17:41,340
[SPEAKER_01] to je dosta teško da Milanović navuče.

2005
01:17:41,340 --> 01:17:43,199
[SPEAKER_01] On isto antagonizira ljude.

2006
01:17:43,199 --> 01:17:46,779
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, probačemo, viječno, ovo je sad pukao na gađenje.

2007
01:17:46,779 --> 01:17:50,979
[SPEAKER_02] Poruka za kraj, jako je riješio.

2008
01:17:50,979 --> 01:17:52,560
[SPEAKER_02] Ništa?

2009
01:17:52,560 --> 01:17:53,420
[SPEAKER_02] Nastavljamo dalje.

2010
01:17:53,420 --> 01:17:56,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa, sad i vi morate, jedno samo,

2011
01:17:56,079 --> 01:17:58,520
[SPEAKER_01] realno svojim trudom i pregnućem,

2012
01:17:58,520 --> 01:18:00,699
[SPEAKER_01] realno podcasti za lokalne izbore.

2013
01:18:00,939 --> 01:18:07,560
[SPEAKER_01] I treba razmišljati, po mojom mišljenju, već polako,

2014
01:18:07,560 --> 01:18:09,600
[SPEAKER_01] kad se medij izgradi,

2015
01:18:09,600 --> 01:18:11,659
[SPEAKER_01] treba razmišljati i o podršci.

2016
01:18:11,659 --> 01:18:15,800
[SPEAKER_01] Treba razmišljati o napravo izrađivanju vrlo jasnih uvjerenja,

2017
01:18:15,800 --> 01:18:18,680
[SPEAKER_01] ono što bi se reklo, media outlet,

2018
01:18:18,680 --> 01:18:20,300
[SPEAKER_01] ili kako to već nazvam, medijskog,

2019
01:18:20,300 --> 01:18:22,420
[SPEAKER_01] vi ste sad ipak jedan medijski,

2020
01:18:22,420 --> 01:18:24,600
[SPEAKER_01] javamo reći tako, jedan proizvod medijski,

2021
01:18:24,600 --> 01:18:27,399
[SPEAKER_01] razmišljati i o podršci.

2022
01:18:27,939 --> 01:18:30,439
[SPEAKER_01] To baš treba biti izrazito oprezan.

2023
01:18:30,439 --> 01:18:33,779
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne treba, ne treba traži nekakvu neutralnost lažno,

2024
01:18:33,779 --> 01:18:34,279
[SPEAKER_01] da se razumijem.

2025
01:18:34,279 --> 01:18:35,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne, to se slaži.

2026
01:18:35,739 --> 01:18:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo lažni, ali samo ljudi znaju naše...

2027
01:18:39,420 --> 01:18:41,600
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, ali treba, treba ići prema...

2028
01:18:41,600 --> 01:18:43,579
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja znam da će to odmah neke ljude odbiti,

2029
01:18:43,579 --> 01:18:45,899
[SPEAKER_01] reći, aj, joj, vi ste sad zagazili na to područje,

2030
01:18:45,899 --> 01:18:47,899
[SPEAKER_01] prljave politike, tako dalje,

2031
01:18:47,899 --> 01:18:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] ali ako se na to ne zagazi,

2032
01:18:49,460 --> 01:18:51,659
[SPEAKER_01] i ako se na to područje ne uđe,

2033
01:18:51,659 --> 01:18:53,220
[SPEAKER_01] praktički ostaviš izolivan.

2034
01:18:53,479 --> 01:18:54,760
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, Jako, ja sve mogu reći,

2035
01:18:54,760 --> 01:18:56,100
[SPEAKER_00] ako se ti kad kandidiraš,

2036
01:18:56,100 --> 01:18:57,239
[SPEAKER_00] izaš, to ja ćete javno.

2037
01:18:57,239 --> 01:18:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, to može.

2038
01:18:58,220 --> 01:19:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] A ove druge sve još moramo proizviti.

2039
01:19:00,720 --> 01:19:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] Treba razmišljati, treba razmišljati

2040
01:19:01,960 --> 01:19:04,399
[SPEAKER_01] i ne treba bježati, ali, od toga, po mojom mišljenju.

2041
01:19:04,399 --> 01:19:05,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ne treba bježati, ovo?

2042
01:19:05,500 --> 01:19:07,340
[SPEAKER_02] Kažemo, opet, treba biti oprezan,

2043
01:19:07,340 --> 01:19:08,720
[SPEAKER_02] naravno, ne predpostavljam,

2044
01:19:08,720 --> 01:19:10,920
[SPEAKER_02] gdje si to i mislio da tu treba biti izrazito oprezan.

2045
01:19:10,920 --> 01:19:11,560
[SPEAKER_02] Pa kod čega?

2046
01:19:11,560 --> 01:19:14,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ali, treba opet na glaze, slika hrvatske vlasti,

2047
01:19:14,640 --> 01:19:16,739
[SPEAKER_02] nažalost, trenutne slike hrvatskog naroda.

2048
01:19:16,739 --> 01:19:19,300
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da, evo, svejedno izađite na izbore.

2049
01:19:19,300 --> 01:19:22,579
[SPEAKER_02] Do toga, duhovna, obitiska, moralna,

2050
01:19:22,579 --> 01:19:24,220
[SPEAKER_02] pa će sve doća svoje.

2051
01:19:24,220 --> 01:19:25,260
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

2052
01:19:25,260 --> 01:19:26,739
[SPEAKER_01] Svako dobro, živjeli.

2053
01:19:26,739 --> 01:19:27,539
[SPEAKER_01] Lijep pozdrav.

